{{Unlicensed}}[[Code Gold]] was a term used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Alliance Intelligence/Legends|intelligence]] [[Division/Legends|division]]. When used in a transmission, it meant that the highest level of information had been obtained, pertaining to the [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] himself.

